Quadraturin 2D graphic engine
=============================

Use Maven to build the project. The build is suited to work in Eclipse SDK environment. 

JOGL overview and links - http://download.java.net/media/jogl/builds/archive/jsr-231-1.1.0/jogl-1.1.0-windows-i586/Userguide.html

JVM params
----------
* Use -ea -Dyarangi.graphics.quadraturin.debug=true to enable debugging.
* Use U-Dsun.awt.noerasebackground=true JVM parameter to disable flickering on aplication's frame resize.
* Use -Dsun.java2d.noddraw=true to disable DirectX for swing (prevent graphic artifacts outside of the GLCanvas).


